Features

Comprehensive Solutions: Each problem is solved using optimal algorithms and data structures, with explanations provided in the comments.

Organized Structure: Problems are categorized into folders based on difficulty (Easy, Medium, Hard) and topic (e.g., Arrays, Linked Lists, Dynamic Programming).

Test Cases: Each solution includes sample test cases and expected outputs.

Efficient Code: Solutions are optimized for performance, utilizing Java's standard library and advanced techniques where applicable.

